{"tid":2265890,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想領養黑貓..","createTime":"2020-10-31T21:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T05:29:25.000Z","uid":94032,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a30b0ebf0d86790394fb6a7199e78b03ee917ca","tid":2265890,"uid":94032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T21:54:28.000Z","msg":"一直想養一隻黑貓 特別係貓女 係一個情意結 細個屋企有養黑貓女自然老死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家人大咗 屋企有三隻貓（一隻買 兩隻領養）但都唔係黑色 <br />\n<br />\n見到香港拯救貓狗協會有隻黑貓女好想領養 可惜佢話我已經有三隻貓容納唔到第四隻 （四人公屋 4百呎左右 一星期5日都係得我同細佬兩個人住）<br />\n<br />\n同埋 有間客房只係用磁貼紋網 細佬拒絕轉做窗花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢都中意貓嘅 平時都會閂實門 行出行入都閂好 養咗十年up都無出意外過 <br />\n<br />\n真係唔想買貓 但又無辦法機構領養 想睇下連登會唔會有一個機會出現 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e68b510e9290cbc0887cd4266895a078084c9c","tid":2265890,"uid":94032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T21:56:26.000Z","msg":"要補充番 兩隻貓貓領養都唔係機構到領養 係咁岩身邊有人需要領養 先咁岩有緣養咗 一隻係病貓棄養 一隻係主人中風急放 所以先養到喳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1b27d3d4a2b967854ad6bdfe62d2c4c7c8efda","tid":2265890,"uid":379992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"絲打你出post而撞啱有黑貓待領養嘅機會未必咁高，可能都係要長期mon住啲貓群/愛協網頁會大啲機會，心誠則靈配合行動，遲早都會遇到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1988095d1f5963394e4f1bb2271e01d79b035c12","tid":2265890,"uid":255802,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T22:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑貓好得意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba92a82487a8ba6ab3836637f03dd783faa18d9","tid":2265890,"uid":94032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1988095d1f5963394e4f1bb2271e01d79b035c12","tid":2265890,"uid":255802,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T22:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑貓好得意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T23:15:38.000Z","msg":"好得意 塊面好圓啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51e8c5d9bf998fdbbd1f65a41ce44799e01c4ed","tid":2265890,"uid":94032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a1b27d3d4a2b967854ad6bdfe62d2c4c7c8efda","tid":2265890,"uid":379992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"絲打你出post而撞啱有黑貓待領養嘅機會未必咁高，可能都係要長期mon住啲貓群/愛協網頁會大啲機會，心誠則靈配合行動，遲早都會遇到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T23:20:09.000Z","msg":"我都明 除咗貓口多之外 客房個窗網都pass唔到義工要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貓群偶然見到黑貓po 都係義工出po <br />\n<br />\n黑貓真係好得意 又神秘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508e0c14c659c35088a58667ec140ad280dcf091","tid":2265890,"uid":117237,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:07:49.000Z","msg":"400呎都要住2個人加3隻貓會唔會太逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想再養不如換樓？住邊區"},{"pid":"eb306495eaa6063f06c71d799aae2662df0562e1","tid":2265890,"uid":218863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flap.org.hk%2Fadoptcat.aspx&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b2015421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n試下睇下lap 見到有隻黑喵Rita <br />\n有朋友喺lap領養過兩隻 義工都好reasonable <br />\n<br />\n希望你可以早日搵到你既主子<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" c